        "content": "## ⏰ AMGO Sports — Post Auto-Expiry\n\n**Workflow F: Daily Cleanup at 7:50 AM AEST**\n\nRuns 10 minutes before Workflow A (8:00 AM) to clean up\nany posts that were never actioned.\n\n**Logic:**\n1. Fetch workflow config from DB settings\n2. Fetch all PENDING posts older than 23 hours\n3. Extract each post ID (returns empty → stops if none)\n4. PATCH each post status to EXPIRED\n5. Send Telegram alert with count\n\n**If no stale posts exist, nothing happens.**",
